headline: Dexcom Stock, Down 13%, Is Haunted By Its 'Surprisingly Cautious' Outlook
summary: Dexcom's solid third-quarter report was overshadowed Friday by its "surprisingly cautious" outlook, and Dexcom stock tumbled.
